Motion sensing / tilting detector

- in forever loop create if else statements
- if Y is less than -500, light up the correct LEDs
- if Y is more than 500, light up the other side
- same for X

Y is tilting up and down (the battery: less than -500 and the USB port: more than 500)
X is tilting on the sides


link:
https://makecode.com/_VHaeAhJdtd6X
